<paragraph blockId="2.[264,1323,1148,1494]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">
In the description of the new species all measurements are given in micrometers (m) and refer to the length of the structure unless otherwise stated. The ventral opisthosomal annuli count starts from the first annulus bordering the genitalia posteriorly. Length of legs is from trochanteral basis to the tip of the tarsus, not including tarsal appendages (solenidia and empodia). For females, each measurement of the 
<typeStatus box="[892,994,1308,1334]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">holotype</typeStatus>
precedes the corresponding range for 
<typeStatus box="[378,494,1348,1374]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">paratypes</typeStatus>
. Some of the measurements of the 
<typeStatus box="[908,1010,1348,1374]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">holotype</typeStatus>
could not be taken becuse of the position it was mounted. All 
<typeStatus box="[716,767,1388,1414]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">type</typeStatus>
specimens are deposited in the collection of Departamento de Entomologia, Fitopatologia e Zoologia Agrícola, Universidade de São Paulo/ 
<collectionCode box="[340,436,1468,1494]" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">ESALQ</collectionCode>
, Piracicaba, São Paulo, 
<collectingCountry box="[718,794,1468,1494]" name="Brazil" pageId="2" pageNumber="57">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
